name: Cave interiors
description: This is a model trained on caves, and caverns. I made this because I thought the default caves looked horrible or nonexistent. May need to increase it starting at 0.6 for desired results. This model was trained on NAI anime-full-pruned and generated in anything5. Made with the Kohya tool for AI Training through google colab. Any suggestions to improve or recommended things for the data set would be appreciated.
